name: Interactive Diagrams Demos

body:
## Paper

[View the paper here](https://mmathys.github.io/maturapaper.pdf)

## Tests

- [layout](/layout/): Two dimensional interactive point/line diagram displaying CO2-emissions (see [14]).

- [layout_finance](/layout_finance/): Same as `layout` but different dataset.

- [3d](/3d/): Three dimensional interactive point diagram (data source: see [14]).
